# Power-BI-_-Credit-cards

Objective - 

To develop a comprehensive credit card weekly dashboard that provides real-time insights into key performance metrics and trends, enabling stakeholders to monitor and analyze credit card operations effectively.

Insights -

1. Overall revenue is 57M
2. Total interest is 8M
3. Total transaction amount is 46M
4. Male customers are contributing more in revenue 31M, female 26M
5. Blue  credit card are contributing to 83% of overall transactions
6. TX, NY & CA is contributing to 68%
7. Overall Activation rate is 57.5%
8. Overall Delinquent rate is 6.06%
9. Overall Delinquent rate is 6.06%
10. Customer of age group 41-50 contribute to 45% of total revenue
11. Graduates contribute to 40% of total revenue
12. Businessman contribute to 31% of total revenue
13. Customers having 2&3 dependents contribute to 55% of total revenue
14. Customers having  salary range of 50K-100K contribute to 32% of total revenue
15. 67% of transactions were done by swiping credit cards


